node.text: We sat down to talk all about her music career for my #OnThatNote series but we talked about everything from music, family, & some of her toughest times! This really felt like it was her time to #SpeakOnIt! Make sure to go to #KandiOnline & turn on your notifications. Believe me you don’t want to miss this interview!

node.text:
I’m proud to be one of the producers of this amazing show @coloredmanplay. Two Grammy nominees, two Tony nominees, a three-time Emmy winner... together on Broadway. Get your tickets today. Link in bio. 
@coloredmanplay @silverthroat  @davinchi  @therealbtc @wolfjames @forrestmcclenson  @dyllonburnside  @mackwilds #ThoughtsofaColoredMan

node.text: My prayers go out to @neneleakes & her family.  @greggleakes was an amazing man who always brought love & great energy to any room he walked into. I’m thankful for the great memories I have of him. Rest in peace Gregg ❤️🙏🏾
